{"article_id":"TLXg0ZjfMQr4auYb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Saturday expressed optimism about his summit with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"but warned","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that the opportunity won ' t happen again ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"calling it a \" one-time shot . \"","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Trump made his remarks in Charlevoix , Canada , at the end of the G-7 summit in a press conference","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"as he prepared to depart for Singapore","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"where he will meet with Kim on Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"to discuss issues such as North Korea denuclearization and an end to the Korean War .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Trump expressed hope","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"that the summit would be good for world peace","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"but also for the dictatorship .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"\" We think","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"North Korea will be a tremendous place in a very short period of time , \"","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"He added","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that the North Korean government was \" working very well \" with the U.S.","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"and said :","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"\" so far so good . \"","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"`` We 'll have to see what happens","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"and we 're going to know very soon . ''","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The road to the summit has been bumpy ,","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"with Trump pulling out of the summit last month after aggressive language from the hermit kingdom .","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"\" You talk about your nuclear capabilities ,","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"but ours are so massive and powerful","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"that I pray to God","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"they will never have to be used , \"","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"he said in a letter to Kim .","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"Trump days later announced","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"that the summit was back on","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"but has remained only cautiously optimistic about how the historic meeting would pan out .","depth":4},{"id":30,"text":"On Saturday , he told reporters","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"while he was optimistic ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Kim would only get one chance .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"\" It ' s unknown territory in the truest sense ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"but I really feel confident , ''","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"`` I feel","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that Kim Jong Un wants to do something great for his people","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"and he has that opportunity","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"and he wo n't have that opportunity again . ''","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"`` It ' s a one-time shot","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"and I think","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"it 's going to work out very well , ''","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"At the end of the presser , he said","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"that the minimum","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"he was hoping for","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"was a relationship and a dialogue .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"When asked how quickly he will know","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"if something good will come of the summit","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"and if Kim was serious ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"he ' d know very quickly .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"As for what issues would be raised at the summit ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"everything will be on the table :","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"\" We ' re going to raise every issue ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"every issue will be raised , \"","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"he said .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":119,"left":79,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nu